high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Place the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed head of lettuce on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter ahead.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Turn around and go forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Clean the lettuce in the sink.
Turn around, then turn left and go to the counter, then turn left to face the counter adjacent to the dishwasher.
Place the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put clean lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the counter.
Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink then pick it back up.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter, turn left again and take a step forward.
Put the clean head of lettuce on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the counter.
